  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowflake Master is your chance to show how to make snowflakes out of paper. There are no limits - just you and your imagination! Save your unique masterpieces and build up a collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/9873f16bb35dbb66621b87a84221e976.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/9873f16bb35dbb66621b87a84221e976.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can try different shapes and colors to bring your idea to reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/1fb7d4e0803fca63d3300ecb63cd72d0.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/1fb7d4e0803fca63d3300ecb63cd72d0.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you just want to relax, there's a library of ready-made patterns for you to repeat. Try it and see how a piece of paper makes beautiful snowflakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/2c82cd4e2914016f777198a0922a93e2.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/2c82cd4e2914016f777198a0922a93e2.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowflake Master is your chance to show how to make snowflakes out of paper. There are no limits - just you and your imagination! Save your unique masterpieces and build up a collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/9873f16bb35dbb66621b87a84221e976.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/9873f16bb35dbb66621b87a84221e976.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can try different shapes and colors to bring your idea to reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/1fb7d4e0803fca63d3300ecb63cd72d0.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/1fb7d4e0803fca63d3300ecb63cd72d0.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you just want to relax, there's a library of ready-made patterns for you to repeat. Try it and see how a piece of paper makes beautiful snowflakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras/2c82cd4e2914016f777198a0922a93e2.avif?t=1739994059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496440/extras_big/2c82cd4e2914016f777198a0922a93e2.avif?t=1739994059 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
